{"tid":689153,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗唔似講笑！歐聯決賽前已嗌走","createTime":"2018-06-04T01:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T04:49:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8947a391ee115bbcfd1a5a6e9fd87d3360fdce69","tid":689153,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:05:54.000Z","msg":"西班牙《馬卡報》爆料，皇家馬德里巨星C朗喺歐聯決賽前1個星期，已經同隊友講過想走，意味佢唔止想扭計加人工咁簡單，考慮離隊唔似講笑。 <br />\n<br />\n知情者話，C朗喺歐聯決賽前1個星期，曾經同隊友講想換新環境，加上皇馬教練施丹突然宣布離隊，令佢更加想走人，因為C朗覺得皇馬換教練後，以目前人腳下季好難拎到西甲或者歐聯冠軍，趁早走最好呀！"},{"pid":"065c4570e23fedc62c6a32857783ef2a86fa1b03","tid":689153,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"去中超啦"},{"pid":"a8b3976afaba4b7abeda112574738ff714797e88","tid":689153,"uid":17680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"回家吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5573f86e1dc4a71caacce56a8c6a98a14389cd45","tid":689153,"uid":10837,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a8b3976afaba4b7abeda112574738ff714797e88","tid":689153,"uid":17680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"回家吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:10:09.000Z","msg":"返士砵亭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca03a883a55c6f7607cd3b59c0533dde5bca9e0","tid":689153,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:11:21.000Z","msg":"過埋疤咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c02722e4828cf84fb9b8aeb7ac46756418f923","tid":689153,"uid":25582,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5573f86e1dc4a71caacce56a8c6a98a